snippet.title: Arcade Game: Crossfire (1975 Atari)
snippet.description:
A 1-on-1 shooting game where each player shoots a ball and push it to the opposite sides to earn points The ball starts at the center of the screen. 

Any interested in trying out this game, here it is:
http://adamulation.blogspot.com/
